# Built binaries
EncodeOverEthernet/Software/ojls_server
EncodeOverEthernet/Software/ojls_client

# Vivado clutter (projects are regenerated from Tcl)
*.jou
*.log
*.str
.Xil/
EncodeOverEthernet/Hardware/pynq-z2/build/
# The PS7 IP writes its config summary to a literal `NA/` when no path is set
EncodeOverEthernet/Hardware/pynq-z2/NA/

# Compiled device tree overlays and bitstream artifacts (built on demand)
*.dtbo
*.bit.bin
# ...except the per-bitness demo bitstreams and the shared overlay, which are
# committed so the HIL sweep and a fresh clone can bring up the board without a
# multi-hour re-synthesis (or even a local dtc). They are build products kept
# in-tree for convenience; the Tcl and .dtso stay the source of truth.
!EncodeOverEthernet/Hardware/pynq-z2/bitstreams/*.bit.bin
!EncodeOverEthernet/Hardware/pynq-z2/openjls.dtbo
